### ========== 每日時刻表管理 API ==========

### 首次儲存時刻表（建立 DailySchedule）
PUT {{betterthanvieshow_HostAddress}}/api/admin/daily-schedules/2025-12-30
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "showtimes": [
    { "movieId": 1, "theaterId": 1, "startTime": "09:45" },
    { "movieId": 1, "theaterId": 2, "startTime": "14:00" },
    { "movieId": 2, "theaterId": 1, "startTime": "17:15" }
  ]
}

### 修改已有時刻表（全部替換）
PUT {{betterthanvieshow_HostAddress}}/api/admin/daily-schedules/2025-12-30
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "showtimes": [
    { "movieId": 1, "theaterId": 1, "startTime": "10:00" },
    { "movieId": 2, "theaterId": 2, "startTime": "15:30" }
  ]
}

### 清空時刻表（傳空陣列）
PUT {{betterthanvieshow_HostAddress}}/api/admin/daily-schedules/2025-12-30
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "showtimes": []
}

### 儲存時刻表失敗 - 電影不存在
PUT {{betterthanvieshow_HostAddress}}/api/admin/daily-schedules/2025-12-30
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "showtimes": [
    { "movieId": 9999, "theaterId": 1, "startTime": "10:00" }
  ]
}

